Body: Description: Is SilverLight still needed on the Netwrix Enterprise Auditor v11.6 any longer? If not we need to remove version 5.1.50918.0

What We've Learned Updated: StealthAUDIT 11.5 and greater does not depend upon Silverlight.
Access Information Center 11.5 and greater (which is an addon to StealthAUDIT) also does not depend upon Silverlight.

Microsoft Silverlight is not required for either of these product versions or greater.
